## Adding new tests

- When you create a new feature or fix a bug, add a new test that will cover the change.

# Running tests

- Run tests via `make test` from repo root to use the Docker sandbox.
- Pass pytest targets after `make test`:
  - `make test core/tests/test_stripe_webhooks.py`
  - `make test core/tests/test_stripe_webhooks.py::test_handle_created_subscription_starts_trial`
- Pass pytest flags after `--`:
  - `make test -- -k trial -q`
- Avoid running `pytest` directly on the host machine.
